        "html": "<style>\n  .bellvane-benefits-section {\n    display: flex;\n    flex-wrap: wrap;\n    gap: 0;\n    margin: 40px 0;\n    border-radius: 12px;\n    overflow: hidden;\n  }\n  .bellvane-benefits-image {\n    flex: 1.2 1 400px;\n    min-height: 350px;\n    background-color: transparent;\n    background-size: cover;\n    background-position: left center;\n  }\n  .bellvane-benefits-text {\n    flex: 1 1 320px;\n    background-color: #A8654E;\n    padding: 40px;\n    display: flex;\n    flex-direction: column;\n    justify-content: center;\n  }\n  .bellvane-benefits-text h2 {\n    font-size: 24px;\n    margin-bottom: 20px;\n    color: #ffffff;\n  }\n  .bellvane-benefit-item {\n    display: flex;\n    align-items: flex-start;\n    gap: 10px;\n    margin-bottom: 16px;\n    color: #ffffff;\n    font-size: 14px;\n    line-height: 1.5;\n  }\n  .bellvane-benefit-check {\n    color: #ffffff;\n    font-weight: 700;\n    flex-shrink: 0;\n  }\n  .bellvane-benefit-item strong {\n    color: #ffffff;\n  }\n\n  .bellvane-faq-section {\n    max-width: 700px;\n    margin: 60px auto;\n    padding: 0 20px;\n  }\n  .bellvane-faq-title {\n    text-align: center;\n    font-size: 22px;\n    margin-bottom: 30px;\n    color: #2B2422;\n  }\n  .bellvane-faq-item {\n    border-bottom: 1px solid #E0D5C8;\n  }\n  .bellvane-faq-question {\n    width: 100%;\n    text-align: left;\n    background: none;\n    border: none;\n    padding: 18px 0;\n    font-size: 15px;\n    font-weight: 600;\n    color: #A8654E;\n    cursor: pointer;\n    display: flex;\n    justify-content: space-between;\n    align-items: center;\n  }\n  .bellvane-faq-answer {\n    max-height: 0;\n    overflow: hidden;\n    transition: max-height 0.3s ease;\n    font-size: 14px;\n    color: #2B2422;\n    line-height: 1.6;\n  }\n  .bellvane-faq-answer-inner {\n    padding-bottom: 18px;\n  }\n  .bellvane-faq-item.active .bellvane-faq-answer {\n    max-height: 200px;\n  }\n  .bellvane-faq-icon {\n    transition: transform 0.3s ease;\n  }\n  .bellvane-faq-item.active .bellvane-faq-icon {\n    transform: rotate(45deg);\n  }\n</style>\n\n<div class=\"bellvane-benefits-section\">\n  <div class=\"bellvane-benefits-image\" style=\"background-image: url('https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0922/9398/8733/files/hf_20260503_035113_948284bb-d9cb-4bf9-8725-7d2cafc880c3.png?v=1782908213');\">\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"bellvane-benefits-text\">\n    <h2>Komfort und Haltung den ganzen Tag.</h2>\n\n    <div class=\"bellvane-benefit-item\">\n      <span class=\"bellvane-benefit-check\">✓</span>\n      <span><strong>Anatomisches X-Rücken-Design</strong>, das die Schultern sanft aufrichtet, ohne Druck oder Zwang.</span>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"bellvane-benefit-item\">\n      <span class=\"bellvane-benefit-check\">✓</span>\n      <span><strong>Nahtloses Nylon-Gewebe</strong>, das unter der Kleidung unsichtbar bleibt und empfindliche Haut schont.</span>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"bellvane-benefit-item\">\n      <span class=\"bellvane-benefit-check\">✓</span>\n      <span><strong>Elastisches Unterbrustband</strong>, das hält, ohne je einzuschneiden oder zu drücken.</span>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"bellvane-faq-section\">\n  <h2 class=\"bellvane-faq-title\">Häufig gestellte Fragen</h2>\n\n  <div class=\"bellvane-faq-item\">\n    <button class=\"bellvane-faq-question\" onclick=\"this.parentElement.classList.toggle('active')\">\n      Hält dieser BH die Brust wirklich den ganzen Tag, ohne Bügel?\n      <span class=\"bellvane-faq-icon\">+</span>\n    </button>\n    <div class=\"bellvane-faq-answer\">\n      <div class=\"bellvane-faq-answer-inner\">\n        Ja, das X-Rücken-Design verteilt den Halt gleichmäßig über Rücken und Schultern, sodass kein Bügel nötig ist.\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n\n  <div class=\"bellvane-faq-item\">\n    <button class=\"bellvane-faq-question\" onclick=\"this.parentElement.classList.toggle('active')\">\n      Wie wähle ich die richtige Größe?\n      <span class=\"bellvane-faq-icon\">+</span>\n    </button>\n    <div class=\"bellvane-faq-answer\">\n      <div class=\"bellvane-faq-answer-inner\">\n        Nutze unsere Größentabelle: S (40-50kg), M (50-60kg), L (60-70kg), XL (70-80kg).\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n\n  <div class=\"bellvane-faq-item\">\n    <button class=\"bellvane-faq-question\" onclick=\"this.parentElement.classList.toggle('active')\">\n      Ist der Stoff für empfindliche Haut geeignet?\n      <span class=\"bellvane-faq-icon\">+</span>\n    </button>\n    <div class=\"bellvane-faq-answer\">\n      <div class=\"bellvane-faq-answer-inner\">\n        Absolut. Der Stoff besteht aus einer Premium-Mischung (75% Nylon, 25% Spandex), die extrem weich, atmungsaktiv und sanft zur Haut ist.\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n\n  <div class=\"bellvane-faq-item\">\n    <button class=\"bellvane-faq-question\" onclick=\"this.parentElement.classList.toggle('active')\">\n      Gibt es eine Geld-zurück-Garantie?\n      <span class=\"bellvane-faq-icon\">+</span>\n    </button>\n    <div class=\"bellvane-faq-answer\">\n      <div class=\"bellvane-faq-answer-inner\">\n        Ja, 30 Tage kostenlose Rückgabe und Umtausch.\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n\n</div>",
